_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/sHjp9bSqzCimGt0fuyaQbZWolA.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/jXMK53gxR71szgGgsIuBDgkKIWa.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":2441,"height":1373,"file_path":"/m5YNcBb3KRgzgT6A5MdgNs6Vcfz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/9X4GvWXBQSMX6kk6EMg8075ECpY.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/iYxzsEBJnFzcgX0amOD6NcaCuPz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.214},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/z44t4V5teiQv9RVNmXD41tAoaNO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.542},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/gaKFXcB5J1gz0QqYj8bWIfrPc04.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.542}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T10:16:25.691+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"First hunt. Last chance.","homepage":"https://www.20thcenturystudios.com/movies/predator-badlands","overview":"Cast out from his clan, a young Predator finds an unlikely ally in a damaged android and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Predador: Terras Selvagens","runtime":107,"tagline":"Primeira caçada. Última chance.","homepage":"https://tickets.disney.com.br/predador-terras-selvagens","overview":"No futuro, em um planeta remoto, um jovem Predador, rejeitado por seu clã, encontra em Thia uma aliada improvável e embarca em uma jornada traiçoeira em busca do adversário supremo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"프레데터: 죽음의 땅","runtime":0,"tagline":"사냥하거나 사냥당하거나","homepage":"","overview":"프레데터로서 존재를 증명하기 위해 우주에서 가장 위험한 행성으로 첫 사냥에 나선 덱. 죽음의 땅에 도사린 모든 것으로부터 공격을 받던 순간, 휴머노이드 티아를 만난다. 최상위 포식자 칼리스크에 맞서게 된 둘은 생존과 각자의 목적을 위해 극한의 사투를 벌이게 되는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Predator : Badlands","runtime":0,"tagline":"Début de la chasse. Dernière chance.","homepage":"","overview":"Jugé trop faible et indigne par son père, chef de la tribu des Yautja, Dek est sur le point de se faire exécuter par son frère Kwei. Mais au dernier moment, celui-ci préfère se sacrifier pour favoriser sa fuite. Décidé à prouver son courage, le jeune paria se rend sur la planète Genna pour y capturer le Kalisk, un monstre réputé invincible. Confronté à une nature hostile et imprévisible, le guerrier inexpérimenté doit sa survie à Thia, une androïde privée de la partie inférieure de son corps depuis son affrontement avec le Kalisk. Avec l'aide de celle-ci, Dek amorce sa traque de la terrible créature, convoitée par des scientifiques pour ses formidables dons de régénération."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.predatorpelicula.es","overview":"Un joven Predator rechazado por su clan encuentra un aliado inesperado en Thia y emprende un peligroso viaje en busca del adversario definitivo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Quái Thú Vô Hình: Vùng Đất Chết Chóc","runtime":0,"tagline":"Cuộc săn đầu tiên. Cơ hội cuối cùng.","homepage":"","overview":"Trong tương lai, tại một hành tinh hẻo lánh, một Predator non nớt - kẻ bị chính tộc của mình ruồng bỏ - tìm thấy một đồng minh không ngờ tới là Thia và bắt đầu hành trình sinh tử nhằm truy tìm kẻ thù tối thượng. Bộ phim do Dan Trachtenberg - đạo diễn của Prey chỉ đạo và nằm trong chuỗi thương hiệu Quái Thú Vô Hình Predator."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Хищник: Планета смерти","runtime":107,"tagline":"«Первая охота. Последний шанс»","homepage":"","overview":"Изгнанный из клана хищник Дек отправляется на опасную планету Генна. Он стремится доказать своему отцу и всему племени, что достоин быть частью клана. Дек встречает загадочную девушку-андроида Тию и объединяется с ней, чтобы отправиться на поиски сверххищника Калиска, наиболее грозного противника на планете."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Predátor: Nebezpečná zóna","runtime":0,"tagline":"Prvý lov. Posledná šanca.","homepage":"","overview":"V ďalekej budúcnosti na vzdialenej planéte mladý Predátor, vyhnanec zo svojho klanu, nájde nečakaného spojenca v Thii a vydávajú sa na zradnú cestu v hľadaní svojho najväčšieho nepriateľa. Predator: Nebezpečná zóna je americký sci-fi akčný film zo série Predátor. Je to siedmy film v hlavnej sérii a deviaty v celkovej sérii, pričom obsahuje aj prvky zo série Votrelec."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Strefa zagrożenia","runtime":106,"tagline":"Pierwsze polowanie. Ostatnia szansa.","homepage":"","overview":"Wygnany ze swojego klanu, obcy łowca i jego nieoczekiwany sojusznik wyruszają w niebezpieczną podróż w poszukiwaniu największego przeciwnika."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"Erste Jagd. Letzte Chance.","homepage":"","overview":"Ein noch junger Predator namens Dek wird von seinem eigenen Clan verstoßen. Die anderen sehen in ihm keinen starken, furchtlosen Krieger heranwachsen. Damit ist er für die Gemeinschaft wertlos, da niemand glaubt, dass Dek eine glorreiche Zukunft bei der Jagd bevorsteht. Fortan muss er also alleine auf einem abgelegenen Planeten klarkommen. Doch dort bleibt er nicht lange alleine. Dek stößt auf Thia mit der er eine unverhoffte Verbündete findet. Von nun an gehen die beiden also gemeinsam auf die Jagd und treffen einen weiteren Weggefährten. Zu dritt müssen sie sich schließlich auch einer scheinbar übermächtigen Bedrohung stellen. Im Laufe ihres gemeinsamen Abenteuers werden sie beste Freunde und lernen, einander auch in ausweglosen Situationen zu vertrauen. Dek wächst dabei als Jäger über sich hinaus und lernt, richtig gut zu jagen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"铁血战士：杀戮之地","runtime":0,"tagline":"初猎，终局","homepage":"","overview":"一名外星猎手被所属部族驱逐后，意外与一台受损的机器人结为盟友，随后踏上险象环生的旅程，寻找自己的终极宿敌。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"พรีเดเตอร์: แดนเถื่อน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"พรีเดเตอร์วัยหนุ่มคนหนึ่งที่ถูกขับไล่ออกจากเผ่าของเขา ได้พบกับมิตรสหายที่ไม่คาดคิด ในการเดินทางเพื่อค้นหาสุดยอดศัตรูของเขา"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"La prima caccia. L'ultima occasione.","homepage":"","overview":"Nel futuro, su un pianeta remoto, un giovane Predatore, emarginato dal suo clan, trova un alleato improbabile in Thia e intraprende un viaggio pericoloso alla ricerca del nemico supremo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Хищникът: Опасна зона","runtime":0,"tagline":"Първи лов. Последен шанс.","homepage":"","overview":"Изгонен от своето племе, един извънземен ловец и неочакван съюзник се впускат в коварно пътешествие в търсене на най-големия си противник."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"鐵血戰士：蠻荒廝殺","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在未來的遙遠星球上，一位被家族放逐的年輕鐵血戰士，流落滿佈全宇宙最兇險異獸的星球，在神秘合成人（艾麗芬寧 飾演）的幫助下展開了一段前所未有的危險旅程，決戰終極獵殺強敵！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"المفترس: الأراضي القاحلة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"بعد أن نُبذ من قبيلته، يسعى صيّاد فضائي لإثبات نفسه واستعادة مكانته، فيتحالف مع رفيق غير متوقّع وينطلقان معًا في رحلة خطرة، بحثًا عن الخصم الأعظم... ذاك الذي قد يمنحه النصر عليه شرفًا مفقودًا، أو يُخلّد سقوطه إلى الأبد."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Padang Pasir","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Seorang Predator muda yang terbuang dari klannya menemukan sekutu yang tidak mungkin dalam perjalanannya mencari musuh utama."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"הטורף: שטח פראי","runtime":0,"tagline":"ציד ראשון. הזדמנות אחרונה.","homepage":"","overview":"בעתיד, על כוכב לכת מרוחק, טורף צעיר שנודה מהשבט שלו נאלץ לחבור לת'יה, אנדרואידית מסתורית, ולצאת למסע באדמות ההפקר בחיפוש אחר היריב האולטימטיבי."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Depredador: Tierras salvajes","runtime":0,"tagline":"Primera cacería. Última oportunidad.","homepage":"","overview":"En el futuro, en un planeta remoto, un joven Depredador, marginado de su clan, encuentra un aliado inesperado en Thia y se embarca en un peligroso viaje en busca del adversario definitivo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"プレデター：バッドランド","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.20thcenturystudios.jp/movies/predator-badlands","overview":"宇宙一ヤバすぎる世界で、追放された若きプレデターと半身アンドロイドの規格外バディが挑む究極のサバイバルSFアクション！\r 誇り高き戦闘一族から追放され、宇宙一危険な“最悪の地＜バッドランド＞”に辿り着いた若き戦士・デク。次々と敵に襲われる彼の前に現れたのは、上半身しかないアンドロイド・ティア。「狩り」に協力すると陽気に申し出た彼女には、ある目的があった･･･。果たして彼は、「究極の敵」を狩って真の「プレデター」になれるのか、それとも「獲物」になってしまうのか。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Хижак: Дикі землі","runtime":0,"tagline":"Перше полювання. Останній шанс.","homepage":"","overview":"Дія розгортається в майбутньому на віддаленій планеті, де молодий Хижак, вигнаний зі свого клану, знаходить малоймовірного союзника в особі Тії та вирушає в підступну подорож на пошуки свого остаточного супротивника."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Vahşi Topraklar","runtime":0,"tagline":"İlk Av. Son Şans.","homepage":"","overview":"Klanından kovulan bir uzaylı avcı ve beklenmedik bir müttefik, nihai düşmanı aramak için tehlikeli bir yolculuğa çıkar."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Prvi lov. Posljednja prilika.","homepage":"","overview":"Izbačen iz klana, lovac na vanzemaljce i neočekivani saveznik kreću na podmuklo putovanje u potrazi za ultimativnim protivnikom."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"მტაცებელი: სასიკვდილო პლანეტა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Predador: Badlands","runtime":0,"tagline":"Primeira caçada. Última oportunidade.","homepage":"","overview":"Expulso do seu clã, um jovem Predador encontra uma aliada improvável e embarca numa viagem traiçoeira, num planeta remoto e mortal, em busca do derradeiro adversário."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Grobuonis: Pavojaus zona","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ateityje, tolimoje planetoje, jaunas plėšrūnas, išvarytas iš savo klano, netikėtai randa sąjungininką ir leidžiasi į pavojingą kelionę, ieškodamas didžiausio priešo. Šioje kelionėje jų laukia ne tik fiziniai išbandymai, bet ir vidinės kovos, kurios atskleidžia drąsos bei ištvermės svarbą atšiauriame pasaulyje, kur išlikimas yra vienintelis tikslas."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Halálbolygó","runtime":0,"tagline":"Első vadászat. Utolsó esély.","homepage":"","overview":"A jövőben, egy távoli bolygón tartózkodó fiatal Ragadozót, Deket száműznek klánjából, mivel túl gyengének tartják. Útja során találkozik egy Thia nevű androiddal, aki a Weyland-Yutani társaság kreálmánya. Szövetséget kötnek és különböző kalandokba keverednek, miközben Dek egy különösen félelmetes lényt üldöz. Izgalmas, újragondolt fejezet a franchise történetében, ami egy jövőbeli, különösen halálos bolygóra, Genna-ra kalauzol minket.  A film legnagyobb ereje a merőben újító szemszögében rejlik, amelyben egy kitaszított Ragadozó kényszerű szövetséget köt egy Weyland szintetikussal. A történet feszes tempójú, ahol egyetlen felesleges perc sincs, garantálva a folyamatos feszültséget. És még a kevésbé akciódús képkockák is hozzáadnak a kerek egészhez."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Predátor: Nebezpečné území","runtime":0,"tagline":"Vítejte ve světě utrpení","homepage":"","overview":"Film se odehrává v budoucnosti na vzdálené planetě, kde mladý Predátor, vyhnaný ze svého klanu, najde nečekanou spojenkyni v syntetické robotické dívce jménem Thia a vydá se na zrádnou cestu za hledáním svého největšího nepřítele."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"終極戰士：殺戮星球","runtime":0,"tagline":"從掠奪者變成獵物，唯有血戰才能生存","homepage":"","overview":"宇宙最強獵人終極戰士身處危機四伏的神祕星球，但這次並非因爲嗜血而大開殺戒，而是因為被逐出家園，被迫展開「獵殺訓練」。唯有如此才能贖回返家的資格。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Prédateur : Badlands","runtime":107,"tagline":"Début de la chasse. Dernière chance.","homepage":"","overview":"Jugé trop faible et indigne par son père, chef de la tribu des Yautja, Dek est sur le point de se faire exécuter par son frère Kwei. Mais au dernier moment, celui-ci préfère se sacrifier pour favoriser sa fuite. Décidé à prouver son courage, le jeune paria se rend sur la planète Genna pour y capturer le Kalisk, un monstre réputé invincible. Confronté à une nature hostile et imprévisible, le guerrier inexpérimenté doit sa survie à Thia, une androïde privée de la partie inférieure de son corps depuis son affrontement avec le Kalisk. Avec l'aide de celle-ci, Dek amorce sa traque de la terrible créature, convoitée par des scientifiques pour ses formidables dons de régénération."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"प्रेडेटर: बैडलैंड्स","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Första jakten. Sista chansen.","homepage":"","overview":"Förvisad av sin egen klan färdas en ung Predator genom dödliga världar i jakten på den ultimata motståndaren och korsar vägar med en oväntad allierad som kan komma att avgöra hans öde."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Mrtva zemlja","runtime":0,"tagline":"Prvi plen. Zadnja možnost.","homepage":"","overview":"Mladi Predator, izobčenec po imenu Dek, se znajde na sovražnem planetu, kjer mora preživeti in si povrniti čast. Na svoji poti Dek sklene nepričakovano zavezništvo s Thio, sintetično androidko korporacije Weyland-Yutani, ki skriva več, kot je sprva videti. Skupaj se podata v boj proti smrtonosnim plenilcem in skrivnostnim silam, ki prežijo v puščavski pokrajini."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Предатор: Дивљина","runtime":0,"tagline":"Први лов. Последња шанса.","homepage":"","overview":"Млади прогнани Предатор покушава да се спасе док се пробија кроз дивљине опасне планете, вежбајући своје вештине у борби са опаким противницима. Циљ му је да победи најсмртоносније створење са којим се његова врста икада суочила, али путовање га одводи до невероватног партнерства када открива постојање још много већег зла."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Plēsoņa: Mežonīgās zemes","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nākotnē, uz tālas planētas no sava klana izraidītais jaunais Plēsoņa atrod negaidītu sabiedroto androida Tijas personā un dodas bīstamā ceļojumā, lai sastaptos ar savu galveno pretinieku."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Predator: Ținuturi sălbatice","runtime":109,"tagline":"Prima vânătoare. Ultima șansă.","homepage":"","overview":"În viitor, pe o planetă îndepărtată, tânărul Predator Dek, izgonit de propriul clan, își găsește un aliat neașteptat în Thia, un android al companiei Weyland-Yutani. Împreună vor porni în căutarea adversarului suprem."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"Eerste jacht. Laatste kans.","homepage":"","overview":"Predator: Badlands, speelt zich af in de toekomst op een afgelegen planeet. Daar sluit een jonge Predator, verstoten door zijn clan, een onverwachte alliantie met Thia en begint aan een gevaarlijke reis op zoek naar de ultieme tegenstander."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Κυνηγός: Επικίνδυνη Ζώνη","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Στο μέλλον, σε έναν απομακρυσμένο πλανήτη, ένας νεαρός Κυνηγός, απόκληρος της φυλής του, βρίσκει έναν απρόσμενο σύμμαχο στην Τία, και ξεκινά ένα επικίνδυνο ταξίδι αναζητώντας τον απόλυτο αντίπαλο."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"غارتگر : سرزمین های بد","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان یک غارتگر که از قبیله خود طرد می‌شود و در سفر خود به‌دنبال یک رقیب شایست، همراه و متحدی غیرقابل انتظار پیدا می‌کند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Predatorit ovat avaruuden metsästäjärotu, joka vaeltaa pitkin universumia etsimässä saalisolentoja, joiden tappaminen ja seinälle ripustaminen kasvattaa pyydystäjän arvostusta ja itsetuntoa. Osoittaakseen arvonsa ja todistaa kykynsä epäilevälle isälleen, nuori yautja-saalistaja Dek lähtee Genna-planeetalle, yhdelle maailmankaikkeuden vaarallisimmista planeetoista metsästämään tappamattomaksi kutsuttua Kaliskia, joka on ollut jo monen predatorin kohtalo. Gennalla Dek törmää Thiaan, Weyland-Yutani -yhtiön androidiin, joka on tiimeineen lähetetty planeetalle tutkimaan paikallisia otuksia, mutta on eksynyt ryhmästään menetettyään alavartalonsa kohdattuaan Kaliskin. Olosuhteiden pakosta Dek joutuu yhdistämään voimansa Thian kanssa."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En un planeta hostil conegut com a Kalisk, un jove Yautja anomenat Dek és expulsat del seu clan després de fallar al seu ritu d'iniciació. Sol i marcat com a presa, el seu destí canvia en trobar Thia, una sintètica danyada de Weyland-Yutani que ha desenvolupat consciència pròpia. Malgrat els seus orígens oposats, formen una aliança infrangible per sobreviure en un entorn on bandes humanes, criatures mutants i altres depredadors els aguaiten. A mesura que Dek busca redimir-se i escalar a la cadena alimentària, descobreix que el seu veritable desafiament no és només caçar, sinó enfrontar una bèstia colossal i gairebé invencible, un kaiju ancestral que representa l'àpex del poder en aquest món destruït. La pel·lícula explora temes d'honor, redempció i connexió entre éssers marginats, oferint una perspectiva inèdita des del punt de vista del Predator."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Udstødt fra sin klan finder en ung Predator en usandsynlig allieret i en beskadiget android og begiver sig ud på en forræderisk rejse på jagt efter den ultimative modstander."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Kiskja: Ohutsoon","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Filmi tegevus toimub kaugel planeedil, kus ühest Kiskjast – noorest ja oma klanni poolt tõrjutud olendist (Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi) – saab noore naise, Thia (Elle Fanning), ootamatu liitlane. Üheskoos alustavad nad ohtlikku ja katsumusterohket teekonda, et leida viimane vastane – ideaalne saak."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"690cfe6af1aaf2deb2ce7842","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/690cfe6af1aaf2deb2ce7842","author":"Manuel São Bento","content":"FULL SPOILER-FREE REVIEW @ https://movieswetextedabout.com/predator-badlands-movie-review-dan-trachtenberg-earns-the-franchise-keys-by-flipping-the-hunt/\r\n\r\n\"Predator: Badlands is an audacious exercise in reinvention that takes a risk and triumphs. The movie excels in every technical department, featuring a spectacle of creature design and sound work, and offering a new thematic vision for the saga's longevity.\r\n\r\nElle Fanning's superb performance and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi's powerful physicality ensure Dek's journey — the creature who forgoes the Yautja code of honor in search of a deeper, collective capability — won't leave anyone indifferent. If there were still doubts that Dan Trachtenberg deserves the keys to the franchise, they've been dissipated once again.\r\n\r\nIt leaves us with the important message that even in the most lethal and solitary of cultures, cooperation and compassion can be the most powerful forms of survival.\"\r\n\r\nRating: B+","created_at":"2025-11-06T20:00:42.420Z","updated_at":"2025-11-06T20:00:42.504Z","author_details":{"name":"Manuel São Bento","rating":7,"username":"msbreviews","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"69136801a4a1c96cc831bd88","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69136801a4a1c96cc831bd88","author":"Chris Sawin","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-11-11T16:44:49.374Z","updated_at":"2025-11-11T16:44:49.450Z","author_details":{"name":"Chris Sawin","rating":9,"username":"ChrisSawin","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"691f018f2b92d38310eb669a","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/691f018f2b92d38310eb669a","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2025-11-20T11:54:55.384Z","updated_at":"2025-11-20T11:54:55.503Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"692ea3ab64eff66050286b68","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/692ea3ab64eff66050286b68","author":"Dave","content":"$13","created_at":"2025-12-02T08:30:35.273Z","updated_at":"2025-12-03T16:58:56.075Z","author_details":{"name":"Dave","rating":8,"username":"dbTMDB88","avatar_path":"/rNHWmW9RqFHW3kN8C1yCFb9BgYR.jpg"}},{"id":"695f341a563563098c3dad46","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/695f341a563563098c3dad46","author":"MovieGuys","content":"$14","created_at":"2026-01-08T04:35:38.879Z","updated_at":"2026-01-26T21:29:59.805Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":5,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"69789930b87343587a695376","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69789930b87343587a695376","author":"daniel_carr","content":"I thought it was a great idea, telling the story of the Predators and their culture! In fact I was hoping for more of that from when \"Predators\" came out. Loved how they tied it in with the \"Alien\" franchise also loved that when they first did it with AVP. But there were a few niggles that killed it for me. Firstly, reading subtitles for too long that really isn't necessary especially when they had a synthetic speaking English anyway, like hello. The idea of Predator has always been the hunt is everything so I can forgive what they did here it was creative but again the story felt off like they were not sure of who the bad guy was. Nice try good ideas just seemed unpolished.","created_at":"2026-01-27T10:53:36.220Z","updated_at":"2026-01-27T10:53:36.228Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"daniel_carr","avatar_path":"/oIZZAY0sYhlk5YHxag5QBTRjoKz.jpg"}},{"id":"697f0f16075105a4d284cd4e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/697f0f16075105a4d284cd4e","author":"Sejian","content":"$15","created_at":"2026-02-01T08:30:14.708Z","updated_at":"2026-02-01T08:36:14.485Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"Sejian","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6991f8d711430905432aee1f","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6991f8d711430905432aee1f","author":"Dean","content":"$16","created_at":"2026-02-15T16:48:23.664Z","updated_at":"2026-02-15T16:48:23.687Z","author_details":{"name":"Dean","rating":10,"username":"Ditendra","avatar_path":"/pbZ9zJZEVYmtmjOZHPRvnnYxqYt.png"}},{"id":"6995185c97f873a609066569","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6995185c97f873a609066569","author":"GenerationofSwine","content":"LOL...I mean, serously.  What is the term the braindead woke zombie goose stepping morons use everytime they trash an IP? Subverting expectations?  Something like that?  Well, they did it again.  Once more they subverted audiance expetations by making a predator movie that's not a predator movie, which, honestly, isn't very shocking.  The last thing Hollywood wants to do at the moment is give the audiance what they want and deliver a Predator movie when they pay to see a Predator movie.\r\n\r\nBut, whatever, it pushes **_THE MESSAGE_**, which makes it the exact same movie as basically every movie since 2016... and, unfortunately, they FAILED to subvert expectations there.  We knew it was going to be woke trash and they gave us woke trash.","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:39:41.046Z","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:39:41.059Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":1,"username":"GenerationofSwine","avata