ote_count":270,"poster_path":"/6Tz1Q69o2n3Zwb0ZffzPL0nFt2T.jpg","release_date":"1959-05-01","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/d3RW7jRsBCHfC9QZaUF9FpzJrh8.jpg","original_title":"অপুর সংসার","original_language":"bn"},{"id":19249,"adult":false,"title":"Holiday on the Buses","video":false,"overview":"Due to a female passenger falling out of her top whilst running for the bus Stan is distracted and crashes the bus resulting in the depot managers car being written off. As a result Stan, Jack and Blakey are fired. Stan and Jack soon get new jobs as a bus crew at a Pontins holiday resort but discover that Blakey has also gotten a job there as the chief security guard.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3969,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/3ewJwuY28E4RzCRf2lklwvzPrsK.jpg","release_date":"1973-05-19","vote_average":7.433,"backdrop_path":"/ePMrWBFymjeEN2nbQsjUdfnusCt.jpg","original_title":"Holiday on the Buses","original_language":"en"},{"id":1086548,"adult":false,"title":"Vera and the Pleasure of Others","video":false,"overview":"Seventeen-year-old Vera earns money by secretly renting out an apartment to teenagers seeking privacy, all while eavesdropping from behind a closed door. As she listens, her own desires awaken.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2507,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/e0ESGyso9K95glbbnTRenFfCC7l.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-26","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/iWb6Kj2qDLPXut8JEvZb2xfwILH.jpg","original_title":"Vera y el placer de los otros","original_language":"es"},{"id":38384,"adult":false,"title":"On the Beat","video":false,"overview":"Norman Pitkin wants to be a policeman like his father was, but he fails the height test (amongst others). One day he gets out his father's old uniform and \"walks the beat\". This leads to a level of chaos that only Pitkin could cause","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3809,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/dLv9QzzQZabT4enXjWEjF8TW1DD.jpg","release_date":"1962-12-11","vote_average":7.683,"backdrop_path":"/w8T3LQTSTy5eAaKgf7dEowQw3Mo.jpg","original_title":"On the Beat","original_language":"en"},{"id":109277,"adult":false,"title":"Death Angel - Sonic German Beatdown - Live in Germany","video":false,"overview":"Five years after the acclaimed comeback album \"The Art Of Dying\", and the following album “Killing Season”, the legendary and one of the most influential bands of the Bay Area Thrash Metal scene DEATH ANGEL will release a DVD with two full length concerts filmed in Germany. The DVD was filmed live at Rockhard Festival 2007 and in Adelsheim.in 2008. It contains some of the new Songs, two Clips and a lot of old DEATH ANGEL stuff which is still seriously cult! This is the first live DVD ever in the history of DEATH ANGEL and it also contains a Live CD. So, what to say more: Grab \"Sonic German Beatdown\" and see by yourself that DEATH ANGEL are more alive than ever before! It's just amazing…","genre_ids":[10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1079,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/p4mYjweSF3uw0QMiGG6DpGuTmyf.jpg","release_date":"2009-05-15","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Death Angel - Sonic German Beatdown - Live in Germany","original_language":"en"},{"id":21991,"adult":false,"title":"State and Main","video":false,"overview":"The residents of a small Vermont town don't know what hit them when a beleaguered Hollywood film crew brings a chaotic shoot to their quaint village.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9714,"vote_count":287,"poster_path":"/348hvpWeSGdAQlCrGvKbpC0FpQN.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-26","vote_average":6.249,"backdrop_path":"/tuerGhZ1lA8wpBjUCEUpeTWDT5B.jpg","original_title":"State and Main","original_language":"en"},{"id":408574,"adult":false,"title":"Chihayafuru: Part II","video":false,"overview":"After successfully won the Tokyo qualifying tournament, Chihaya and her friends are set to go on to the nationals. As they prepare, Chihaya is faced with new personal issues as her childhood friend and inspiration, Arata, has announced that he has quit competitive karuta. Not only that, but a new rival emerges in the reigning female champion karuta player, Shinobu Wakamiya, a karuta prodigy who became the nation's and the world's greatest female karuta player as a 9th grader. All of this forces Chihaya to reexamine her love of the game in the midst of preparing for one of the biggest tournaments of the year.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.894,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/fH9ze51RlYmbdMjO8csrfCb32TW.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-29","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/1QhVu5Hj6UmiKHTd7Xq3hL5Llq6.jpg","original_title":"ちはやふる 下の句","original_language":"ja"},{"id":520765,"adult":false,"title":"Go!","video":false,"overview":"Jack is a charismatic larrikin who has just discovered the one thing he's really good at — go-kart racing. With the support of his mentor, Patrick, an old race car driver with a secret past, and his best mates Colin and Mandy, Jack must learn to control his recklessness if he is to defeat the best drivers in Australia, including the ruthless champion Dean, and win the National title.","genre_ids":[10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6976,"vote_count":328,"poster_path":"/jnOSpITigPAG2SvmoxTSFJy35sv.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-16","vote_average":6.822,"backdrop_path":"/hRgQVdKh65nFiy2l7KhfWo7DHof.jpg","original_title":"Go!","original_language":"en"},{"id":262903,"adult":false,"title":"Main Tera Hero","video":false,"overview":"Seenu loves Sunaina but they're chased by a stalking cop, an infatuated beauty and her mafia don dad - can Seenu's heroics work?","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4194,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/bupZH3i1SAaLLC0OgYMSLDZN63Q.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-04","vote_average":5.667,"backdrop_path":"/wgYx4MwezeoAkRVAJsYdOMAMeWC.jpg","original_title":"मैं तेरा हीरो","original_language":"hi"},{"id":110552,"