ied by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it's absolutely impossible to contain.","genre_ids":[27,53,878],"popularity":16.2528,"vote_count":8234,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.237,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":419261,"adult":false,"title":"Earthtastrophe","video":false,"overview":"In a white hot flash of light, and with no warning, one minute our moon is there, the next it's gone. Then, a second flash. And that's the last thing anyone on Earth can remember. 11 months later, it's not post- apocalyptic; it's apocalyptic as Earth has been sucked through a wormhole, literally ripping our planet from the inside out. With bizarre disasters and civilization collapsing, our heroes must find a way to survive and get to \"safe ground\" before it's too late.","genre_ids":[878,10770],"popularity":2.667,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/PdO6DOQktCGtPeZRrtOZhtvjWf.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-05","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/q9VrDrEO55HppFzEchAmHfGH1Qw.jpg","original_title":"Earthtastrophe","original_language":"en"},{"id":646,"adult":false,"title":"Dr. No","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 battles mysterious Dr. No, a scientific genius bent on destroying the U.S. space program. As the countdown to disaster begins, Bond must go to Jamaica, where he encounters beautiful Honey Ryder, to confront a megalomaniacal villain in his massive island headquarters.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":7.2117,"vote_count":3954,"poster_path":"/f9HsemSsBEHN5eoMble1bj6fDxs.jpg","release_date":"1962-10-07","vote_average":6.99,"backdrop_path":"/ptcXbbxTyjHfEE4d4QocNP0YQct.jpg","original_title":"Dr. No","original_language":"en"},{"id":657,"adult":false,"title":"From Russia with Love","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 is back in the second installment of the James Bond series, this time battling a secret crime organization known as SPECTRE. Russians Rosa Klebb and Kronsteen are out to snatch a decoding device known as the Lektor, using the ravishing Tatiana to lure Bond into helping them. Bond willingly travels to meet Tatiana in Istanbul, where he must rely on his wits to escape with his life in a series of deadly encounters with the enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":6.5294,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/zx4V17FP8oclNvOpTgs2iCCtiYk.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-10","vote_average":7.065,"backdrop_path":"/8JMiQa0OqsCYvbNUrQIrMzwV7g2.jpg","original_title":"From Russia with Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":658,"adult":false,"title":"Goldfinger","video":false,"overview":"Special agent 007 comes face to face with one of the most notorious villains of all time, and now he must outwit and outgun the powerful tycoon to prevent him from cashing in on a devious scheme to raid Fort Knox -- and obliterate the world's economy.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":6.2145,"vote_count":3869,"poster_path":"/aKNFzaqQgPzsGXnsMc4kJH5hFIV.jpg","release_date":"1964-09-20","vote_average":7.355,"backdrop_path":"/f1Is9VLQZSRpeLMU7mIcj5aXclt.jpg","original_title":"Goldfinger","original_language":"en"},{"id":691,"adult":false,"title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","video":false,"overview":"Russian and British submarines with nuclear missiles on board both vanish from sight without a trace. England and Russia both blame each other as James Bond tries to solve the riddle of the disappearing ships. But the KGB also has an agent on the case.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.5757,"vote_count":2165,"poster_path":"/3ZxHKFxMYvAko680DsRgAZKWcLi.jpg","release_date":"1977-07-07","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/8lRdfsmJjUXQU3DMOOB3vVIhJxP.jpg","original_title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":754,"adult":false,"title":"Face/Off","video":false,"overview":"In order to foil a terrorist plot, an FBI agent undergoes facial transplant surgery and assumes the identity of a criminal mastermind. The plan turns sour when the criminal wakes up prematurely and seeks revenge.","genre_ids":[28,80,878],"popularity":6.5992,"vote_count":5766,"poster_path":"/69Xzn8UdPbVnmqSChKz2RTpoNfB.jpg","release_date":"1997-06-27","vote_average":7.052,"backdrop_path":"/tsSWHgaFlzzkp3o976juBZbmcs2.jpg","original_title":"Face/Off","original_language":"en"},{"id":950494,"adult":false,"title":"PJ Masks: We Can All Be Heroes","video":true,"overview":"National Superhero Day is April 28 and we’re celebrating early with the PJ Masks! Wear your pajamas to watch Catboy, Owlette, and Gekko take on their toughest missions yet and discover what really makes a hero. This screening includes an epic 4–part special, plus music videos, other super episodes, and even an exciting PJ Masks sneak peek!","genre_ids":[28,12,16,10751,14,878],"popularity":0.1336,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/cGRIIasLzHUEKcoVXK2kgWiW6B0.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-23","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"PJ Masks: We Can All Be Heroes","original_language":"en"},{"id":924,"adult":false,"title":"Dawn of the Dead","video":false,"overview":"A group of survivors take refuge in a shopping mall after the world is taken over by aggressive, flesh-eating zombies.","genre_ids":[27,28],"popularity":6.7959,"vote_count":4359,"poster_path":"/ttquyxStEEctzghtA2f4PUGprDr.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-19","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/rspbS1E9wJtslrb8amfJgtMBUVh.jpg","original_title":"Dawn of the Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":787,"adult":false,"title":"Mr. & Mrs. Smith","video":false,"overview":"A husband and wife struggle to keep their marriage alive until they realize they are both secretly working as assassins. Now, their respective assignments require them to kill each other.","genre_ids":[28,35,18,53],"popularity":7.8045,"vote_count":11037,"poster_path":"/kjD700RtyhveN3ZbOnSvUSne0Qj.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-07","vote_average":6.69,"backdrop_path":"/2YJOXPl4QtCskixYA58ToyCXEW0.jpg","original_title":"Mr. & Mrs. Smith","original_language":"en"},{"id":830,"adult":false,"title":"Forbidden Planet","video":false,"overview":"Starship C57D travels to planet Altair 4 in search of the crew of spaceship \"Bellerophon,\" a scientific expedition that has been missing for twenty years. They find themselves unwelcome by the expedition's lone survivor and warned of destruction by an invisible force if they don't turn back immediately.","genre_ids":[878,12],"popularity":2.3174,"vote_count":1028,"poster_path":"/aq0OQfRS7hDDI8vyD0ICbH9eguC.jpg","release_date":"1956-03-02","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/9EUmwXS6EbY5djAhLtBGzUbBwNV.jpg","original_title":"Forbidden Planet","original_language":"en"},{"id":841,"adult":false,"title":"Dune","video":false,"overview":"In the year 10,191, the most precious substance in the universe is the spice Melange. The spice extends life. The spice expands consciousness. The spice is vital to space travel.  The spice exists on only one planet in the entire universe, the vast desert planet Arrakis, also known as Dune.  Its native inhabitants, the Fremen, have long held a prophecy that a man would come, a messiah who would lead them to true freedom.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"popularity":6.5146,"vote_count":3340,"poster_path":"/4kJmUCE7mkVJjXa7A0g2rY4IGTm.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-14","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/5wJ2tckpvwcxGCAgZiccodwEJpf.jpg","original_title":"Dune","original_language":"en"},{"id":864,"adult":false,"title":"Cool Runnings","video":false,"overview":"When a Jamaican sprinter is disqualified from the Olympic Games, he enlists the help of a dishonored coach to start the first Jamaican bobsled team.","genre_ids":[35,12,18],"popularity":7.2738,"vote_count":2226,"poster_path":"/6fXuGEb7EqGmAeUodxm7l5ELPZ.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-01","vote_average":7.004,"backdrop_path":"/ucFDgf7Nw6cEwPh5o4cacp3k1aW.jpg","original_title":"Cool Runnings","original_language":"en"},{"id":869,"adult":false,"title":"Planet of the Apes","video":false,"overview":"After a spectacular crash-landing on an uncharted planet, brash astronaut Leo Davidson finds himself trapped in a savage world where talking apes dominate the human race. Desperate to find a way home, Leo must evade the invincible gorilla army led by Ruthless General Thade.","genre_ids":[53,878,28,12],"popularity":4.961,"vote_count":4330,"poster_path":"/eEsOgbgKXMvI2FEw1WENamVXi41.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-26","vote_average":5.762,"backdrop_path":"/1N0MYYFvYwpM5fi3mjw4150ReoR.jpg","original_title":"Planet of the Apes","original_language":"en"},{"id":488,"adult":false,"title":"The African Queen","video":false,"overview":"At the start of the First World War, in the middle of Africa’s nowhere, a gin soaked riverboat captain is persuaded by a strong-willed missionary to go down river and face-off a German warship.","genre_ids":[10749,12,18],"popularity":2.3698,"vote_count":1027,"poster_path":"/2Ypg0KhQfFYWILelvHGtSHHR0dk.jpg","release_date":"1952-01-07","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/doTKdtLfn2b7ZmeElmT6ZDW3XIk.jpg","original_title":"The African Queen","original_language":"en"},{"id":503,"adult":false,"title":"Poseidon","video":false,"overview":"A packed cruise ship traveling the Atlantic is hit and overturned by a massive wave, compelling the passengers to begin a dramatic fight for their lives.","genre_ids":[12,28,18,53],"popularity":3.4635,"vote_count":2254,"poster_path":"/fDPdjGc8SUEDWfTwMaZlCE6NSi3.jpg","release_date":"2006-05-03","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/cmif4raVnSublaj6wEswHHPPL65.jpg","original_title":"Poseidon","original_language":"en"},{"id":330,"adult":false,"title":"The Lost World: Jurassic Park","video":false,"overview":"Four years after Jurassic Park's genetically bred dinosaurs ran amok, multimillionaire John Hammond shocks chaos theorist Ian Malcolm by revealing that he has been breeding more beasties at a secret location. Malcolm, his paleontologist ladylove and a wildlife videog